title: Proposal: Deploy Cauldrons and Degenbox on BSC
body:
**Proposal to Deploy Cauldrons and Degenbox on BSC**

Binance Smart Chain is the first chain that really started the EVM compatibility ecosystem. Currently BSC is seeing 1.6M Daily Active Addresses with a total of $20B TVL being onchain, this is obviously a substantial amount. With Abracadabra moving to BSC, we could capture more TVL, new assets and completely new users.

Needless to say, the Binance Smart Chain Ecosystem Fund of $1 Billion that was recently announced will very likely further increase adoption of the chain and also further grow TVL.

Abracadabra.money is a multichain project and because of this it is a no brainer to deploy on BSC as it is the second largest chain in this EVM ecosystem.
